steps:


CI/CD Pipeline Assignment (Git + Docker + Kubernetes + Jenkins)

1. Create Git Repository & Files:(VSCOde)

git init
touch index.html Dockerfile deployment.yaml

index.html:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>CI/CD Demo</title>
<style>
body{
text-align:center;
font-family:Times New Roman;
background-color:#af0d0d;
}
h1{
color:#0ef777;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>CI/CD Pipeline Working</h1>
